## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of sources accessed. Some sources may not reflect the most current developments due to publication dates. Additionally, the perspectives included are primarily from Western contexts, which may not fully represent global views on gender identity evolution. Further research could explore more diverse cultural perspectives and the impact of legal and policy changes on gender identity recognition.